:272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ba6a8968faced0bf0e43e86fb799b909edf413a","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6f900b3ae2a4901656dd55e78398f773d4ee519","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n其實又唔需要，你其實點解想考翻DSE?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年冇讀書，拿返五科合格，數學最無頭緒入手</blockquote><br />\n咁啫係其實你想重考所有科目 ，包括中英數通識以及一科選修課？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要數學，之前讀毅進，五科合格但不包括數學</blockquote><br />\n但係其實完成毅進文憑就等於資歷架構第三等級，相等於5個二，包括中英數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n咁記住雖然2018年dse報名日期未公佈，但通常都會係九月初開始報名，只要你合乎dae自修生考生嘅報名資格，就可以以自修生嘅身份報考2018年文憑試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝謝 ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb67a88a7d0b87370fd54f32e125484c5cde1aee","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n其實又唔需要，你其實點解想考翻DSE?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年冇讀書，拿返五科合格，數學最無頭緒入手</blockquote><br />\n咁啫係其實你想重考所有科目 ，包括中英數通識以及一科選修課？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要數學，之前讀毅進，五科合格但不包括數學</blockquote><br />\n但係其實完成毅進文憑就等於資歷架構第三等級，相等於5個二，包括中英數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n用私人立場非輔導員身份同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩連讀毅進都drop數咁睇唔開啊😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀完問過唔包括數學<br />\n<br />\n要你另外讀<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49711bd8f82c7d53879505da5503c054408b9845","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3da171f0824046de85c07fec83991bc03c3f7e7b","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年冇讀書，拿返五科合格，數學最無頭緒入手</blockquote><br />\n咁啫係其實你想重考所有科目 ，包括中英數通識以及一科選修課？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要數學，之前讀毅進，五科合格但不包括數學</blockquote><br />\n但係其實完成毅進文憑就等於資歷架構第三等級，相等於5個二，包括中英數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n咁記住雖然2018年dse報名日期未公佈，但通常都會係九月初開始報名，只要你合乎dae自修生考生嘅報名資格，就可以以自修生嘅身份報考2018年文憑試</blockquote><br />\n而且留意翻，文憑試嘅數學同會考數學課程係唔一樣，我覺得你可以考慮報讀市面上嘅一些數學補底課程，同埋考慮購買新嘅參考書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n需要買返dse 既 pp 嗎？新款cal 機會唔會同舊機差好多？<br />\n用緊黑色cal 機"},{"pid":"12d1252145e66d3ab24fe4f6e0ce9231fdd24845","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"咁都負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到明求助post"},{"pid":"a118a970fca2698ccfab5dd2c3e16dbce9deea9e","tid":272242,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"讀黎做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc883f0b8b821b45be021d839e4511680ee41c4c","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d03e000f3d13f7a63db995d1f62b35acd08bd4a8","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:24:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a8ed10e45b75afd434375f9205ef196d6f41aeb","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咁啫係其實你想重考所有科目 ，包括中英數通識以及一科選修課？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要數學，之前讀毅進，五科合格但不包括數學</blockquote><br />\n但係其實完成毅進文憑就等於資歷架構第三等級，相等於5個二，包括中英數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n用私人立場非輔導員身份同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩連讀毅進都drop數咁睇唔開啊😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀完問過唔包括數學<br />\n<br />\n要你另外讀<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁下次選擇課程記得睇同問清楚😂<br />\n但留意翻，毅進文憑嘅學歷係唔可以同dse or 會考成績合拼，就算你數學最後考到4，你都唔可以將自己嘅學歷當係22422，再用依個成績報讀其他專上課程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪要逐科考過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435985d17e31376d0c20b128930b7ad6293c4d3e","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要數學，之前讀毅進，五科合格但不包括數學</blockquote><br />\n但係其實完成毅進文憑就等於資歷架構第三等級，相等於5個二，包括中英數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n咁記住雖然2018年dse報名日期未公佈，但通常都會係九月初開始報名，只要你合乎dae自修生考生嘅報名資格，就可以以自修生嘅身份報考2018年文憑試</blockquote><br />\n而且留意翻，文憑試嘅數學同會考數學課程係唔一樣，我覺得你可以考慮報讀市面上嘅一些數學補底課程，同埋考慮購買新嘅參考書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n需要買返dse 既 pp 嗎？新款cal 機會唔會同舊機差好多？<br />\n用緊黑色cal 機</blockquote><br />\n如果你覺得有需要，可以購買新一屆嘅dse pp操練，而計算機，新款的計算機其實多出的功能你也在dse用不著，但個人認為你部計算機至少要fx-3650或以上先應付到文憑試，而我用嘅係fx-50fh ii</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好<br />\n再問問，dse 成績是否永久"},{"pid":"319b218ed4c5c04d42f4054f330d0cda10c51823","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c39f5321b498316b220758c7d0c5851bb429a55b","tid":272242,"uid":68641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"卷一 part A盡執<br />\n MC唔太差<br />\n拎2唔難既"},{"pid":"833fc8682885e9e7eca19276916eac59d4af1fbf","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a2e2e354abc20578f8bb69ee59b47d6b0847a18","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed804dff02a547109fdd831a531dda0203b56375","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b65eb12f0ad42f00b121a2041ec630f156be8109","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n用私人立場非輔導員身份同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩連讀毅進都drop數咁睇唔開啊😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀完問過唔包括數學<br />\n<br />\n要你另外讀<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁下次選擇課程記得睇同問清楚😂<br />\n但留意翻，毅進文憑嘅學歷係唔可以同dse or 會考成績合拼，就算你數學最後考到4，你都唔可以將自己嘅學歷當係22422，再用依個成績報讀其他專上課程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪要逐科考過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你逐科考你真係確認你可以一年就可以溫到其他人學六年嘅野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時來說 信心不大<br />\n盡早開始<br />\n如果自修生開始接受報名的時候<br />\n進度不太理想<br />\n可能要延遲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be7bf7cfb962a03d7f2ee26e175ffe82621114d","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卷一 part A盡執<br />\n MC唔太差<br />\n拎2唔難既</blockquote><br />\n好多人都講mc 可以夠合格"},{"pid":"47c915d5858f04e55696e198ab6cb143277a9c03","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進既話要再修讀延伸數學科。<br />\n反正都是一樣，倒不如dse</blockquote><br />\n咁記住雖然2018年dse報名日期未公佈，但通常都會係九月初開始報名，只要你合乎dae自修生考生嘅報名資格，就可以以自修生嘅身份報考2018年文憑試</blockquote><br />\n而且留意翻，文憑試嘅數學同會考數學課程係唔一樣，我覺得你可以考慮報讀市面上嘅一些數學補底課程，同埋考慮購買新嘅參考書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n需要買返dse 既 pp 嗎？新款cal 機會唔會同舊機差好多？<br />\n用緊黑色cal 機</blockquote><br />\n如果你覺得有需要，可以購買新一屆嘅dse pp操練，而計算機，新款的計算機其實多出的功能你也在dse用不著，但個人認為你部計算機至少要fx-3650或以上先應付到文憑試，而我用嘅係fx-50fh ii</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好<br />\n再問問，dse 成績是否永久</blockquote><br />\ndse成績成績係永久，但報讀專上課程只接受近一至兩年的dse成績，有部分學院甚至不接受非當屆DSE成績，視乎該學院嘅規定</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白<br />\n時間是最大敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507078e95edd3ee86c7b64207b3fd2191685f352","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3413e6a200f5c2c0cdff3cb3396a3352403bd0e1","tid":272242,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:50:24.000Z","msg":"DSE難過會考喎<br />\n樓主加油"},{"pid":"c0f0dbb9264bfbee5169f678621b9046b33a3978","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n用私人立場非輔導員身份同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩連讀毅進都drop數咁睇唔開啊😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀完問過唔包括數學<br />\n<br />\n要你另外讀<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁下次選擇課程記得睇同問清楚😂<br />\n但留意翻，毅進文憑嘅學歷係唔可以同dse or 會考成績合拼，就算你數學最後考到4，你都唔可以將自己嘅學歷當係22422，再用依個成績報讀其他專上課程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪要逐科考過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你逐科考你真係確認你可以一年就可以溫到其他人學六年嘅野？</blockquote><br />\n小建議：如果目標唔係繼續升學，我建議你都係權衡利弊，因為自修生重考其實都唔平（綜援可申請退款），每份卷都500，而語文課更加係700一份卷，兩科合共10份卷，連其他副科，分分鐘真係需要1萬以上，而且付出嘅時間都好多，但如果目標係為左升學嘅，記得報翻jupas同E-app，記住，只要有心，從來都唔會怕遲！加油！期望出年可以見到巴打開post宣佈好消息🙂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會好好考慮，謝謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da47b15d8a6a474d45cecb71bcf3d9f3b34890b3","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78a33cad0a57676f8539ef4c2687e070f3c143a9","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>卷一 part A盡執<br />\n MC唔太差<br />\n拎2唔難既</blockquote><br />\n好多人都講mc 可以夠合格</blockquote><br />\n只能說別太相信這句話<br />\n雖然dse合格真係唔難，但數學想合格至少都要確認自己識做到乙一先算穩合格，因為如果乙一都唔識做，我相信都幾難合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好，明天去買教科書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由明天開始"},{"pid":"b9879a2102e3b48ed2ac20b9e8a6bbce551ab628","tid":272242,"uid":60415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"<bloc