/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你逐科考你真係確認你可以一年就可以溫到其他人學六年嘅野？</blockquote><br />\n小建議：如果目標唔係繼續升學，我建議你都係權衡利弊，因為自修生重考其實都唔平（綜援可申請退款），每份卷都500，而語文課更加係700一份卷，兩科合共10份卷，連其他副科，分分鐘真係需要1萬以上，而且付出嘅時間都好多，但如果目標係為左升學嘅，記得報翻jupas同E-app，記住，只要有心，從來都唔會怕遲！加油！期望出年可以見到巴打開post宣佈好消息🙂</blockquote><br />\n其實到底你對dse認知有幾多<br />\n自修生就算考曬7科都係三四千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考一科先 應該唔洗一千銀掛"},{"pid":"c09bcfeb978ad5b915eea1ae2368afad70be28a3","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T18:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Tommy?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不是 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978340860264d001729a6c9e6f950f20e233c709","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:54:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"681893d54a1acb5635ed1a80f50340266764c2f9","tid":272242,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebc18205f53685a87378eb55276ffd1e411dc3e8","tid":272242,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:31:35.000Z","msg":"操多幾年past paper<br />\n有閒錢可以搵個識教既私補<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油 數學一理通百理明"},{"pid":"1155567a2e01b4dcc5d2a7140a84119766c40db7","tid":272242,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"淨考數學？"},{"pid":"723cf55a7ec3918e26aaaa3e60c496889bc8922c","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨考數學？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為都返緊工 最主要差呢科<br />\n想搞好呢科先<br />\n主要目的不是為升學"},{"pid":"eabb93d1ad7a91e0df3f41592893fcc74a19f295","tid":272242,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>